gwtupload.server
Class UploadListener

java.lang.Object
  gwtupload.server.AbstractUploadListener
      gwtupload.server.UploadListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, org.apache.commons.fileupload.ProgressListener
public class UploadListener
extends AbstractUploadListener

This is a File Upload Listener that is used by Apache Commons File Upload to monitor the progress of the uploaded file. This object and its attributes have to be serializable because Google App-Engine uses dataStore and memCache to store session objects.
